<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 12:54:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Kraken 部署 AI 后裁员 150 人； IPO 可能推迟至 2027 年</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/kraken-cuts-150-workers-after-deploying-ai-ipo-may-slip-to-2027</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，全球最古老的加密货币交易所之一 Kraken 已裁员以降低成本，并且由于数字资产价格大幅下跌，Kraken 可能不会像最初预期的那样尽快上市。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIHcsH.4r5jA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 18:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/kraken-cuts-150-workers-after-deploying-ai-ipo-may-slip-to-2027</guid></item><item><title>加密货币在具有里程碑意义的立法上的胜利重塑了与银行的竞争</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/crypto-s-win-on-landmark-legislation-reshapes-rivalry-with-banks</link><description>多年来，大银行一直致力于将加密货币排除在主流金融之外，理由包括洗钱、欺诈和稳定性风险等各种问题，并认为如果没有银行同等的监管，该行业就无法享受银行般的特权。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRuS46AYKU1U/v3/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 17:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/crypto-s-win-on-landmark-legislation-reshapes-rivalry-with-banks</guid></item><item><title>CME、ICE 敦促美国遏制加密货币石油交易新贵</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/cme-ice-push-us-to-curb-crypto-s-offshore-oil-trading-upstart</link><description>洲际交易所和芝商所正在敦促美国控制 Hyperliquid，这是一个快速增长且不受监管的加密平台，交易所表示可能会扭曲全球油价并被用于操纵价格。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iITwUdbypwk0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 12:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/cme-ice-push-us-to-curb-crypto-s-offshore-oil-trading-upstart</guid></item><item><title>由于通胀担忧打击风险资产，比特币跌破 79,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/bitcoin-dips-below-79-000-as-inflation-fears-hit-risk-assets</link><description>由于对通货膨胀和高油价的担忧令投资者感到不安，股票等风险资产的抛售席卷了加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUMafSsucPlw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 14:36:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/bitcoin-dips-below-79-000-as-inflation-fears-hit-risk-assets</guid></item><item><title>Winklevosses 向饱受打击的 Gemini 交易所投资 1 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/winklevosses-invest-100-million-in-battered-gemini-exchange</link><description>创立 Gemini Space Station Inc. 的亿万富翁双胞胎泰勒·文克莱沃斯 (Tyler Winklevoss) 和卡梅伦·温克莱沃斯 (Cameron Winklevoss) 对这家亏损的加密货币交易所进行了 1 亿美元的“战略投资”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyH6RCEPUEe0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/winklevosses-invest-100-million-in-battered-gemini-exchange</guid></item><item><title>代币化正在金融领域最不性感的角落被拥抱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-14/tokenization-is-catching-on-in-the-least-sexy-corner-of-finance-repo</link><description>区块链在回购市场中的使用正在蓬勃发展。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5Bcso_KIQgM/v18/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-14/tokenization-is-catching-on-in-the-least-sexy-corner-of-finance-repo</guid></item><item><title>加密货币亿万富翁加入投资者的行列，押注委内瑞拉高风险以获得巨额回报</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/crypto-billionaire-ehrsam-joins-risky-bet-on-venezuela-revival</link><description>美国加密货币亿万富翁 Fred Ehrsam 已成为吸引委内瑞拉的最引人注目、最引人注目的外国投资者之一，他押注这个饱受制裁的国家可能会在其遭受重创的经济重新开放时提供巨额回报。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCc_7HRlPruQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 18:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/crypto-billionaire-ehrsam-joins-risky-bet-on-venezuela-revival</guid></item><item><title>随着加密货币市场监管法案的推进，比特币突破 80,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/bitcoin-stalls-as-crypto-gains-ground-in-washington-wall-street</link><description>参议院银行委员会经过数月的谈判提出了具有里程碑意义的美国数字资产市场结构法案后，比特币价格攀升至 80,000 美元以上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipACoh5nEXcw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 14:58:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/bitcoin-stalls-as-crypto-gains-ground-in-washington-wall-street</guid></item></channel></rss>